BUGS
====

- bash-completer needs to become endpoint aware by scanning for -e <ENDPOINT>

- rmdir: Handle pagination for clear_container


FEATURES
========

- Named-endpoints

# Use default endpoint
bashfiles get container foo

equivalent to

bashfiles -e default get container foo

# Use 'bar' endpoint
bashfiles -e bar get container foo

OPTION 2a

- Source general config
- Source endpoint config

~/.bashfiles/
    config
    endpoints/
        default
            CF_USERNAME=myuser
        s3
            S3_USERNAME=myuser
    completion/
        default/
            container-names
            <container>-object-names


CRUD:

bashfiles endpoints ls
bashfiles endpoints add bar
bashfiles endpoints rm bar





